---
layout: layout.njk
---
<!-- Hero Section -->
          <section
            class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-40 pb-20 text-center overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
              <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
                <img
                  src="img/FullLogo.svg"
                  alt="Kaasi Logo"
                  class="h-12 md:h-16 mx-auto mb-8"
                  onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/200x64/121212/e67e26?text=Kaasi&font=satoshi';"
                />
                <h1
                  class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight"
                >
                  The Lankan Finance Manager 🇱🇰
                </h1>
                <p
                  class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10"
                >
                  Track expenses, manage accounts, and see where your money
                  goes. Kaasi is a simple, private, and powerful tool to master
                  your LKR.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
                  <a
                    href="https://app.kaasi.com.lk/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="cta-button-large"
                  >
                    Launch Kaasi
                  </a>
                  <a href="#features" class="cta-button-secondary">
                    Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-down ml-2 text-xs"></i>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- App Mockup -->
              <div class="mt-20 animate-fade-in-up" style="--delay: 0.3s">
                <div
                  id="mockup-container"
                  class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl"
                >
                  <div class="absolute -inset-2">
                    <div
                      class="w-full h-full max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 via-orange-400 to-orange-600 opacity-10 blur-3xl"
                    ></div>
                  </div>
                  <img
                    id="mockup-image"
                    src="img/dash.png"
                    onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/1200x600/18181b/3f3f46?text=Kaasi+Dashboard';"
                    alt="Kaasi App Dashboard Mockup"
                    class="relative w-full h-auto object-cover object-top rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-800/80 shadow-2xl shadow-black/80"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Features Section (Bento Grid) -->
          <section id="features" class="py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
              <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2
                  class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 animate-on-scroll"
                >
                  A Powerful Toolkit for Your Rupees
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="text-lg text-gray-400 animate-on-scroll"
                  style="--delay: 0.1s"
                >
                  Everything you need to be in control of your financial life.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                <!-- Top Row -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                  <div class="bento-card lg:col-span-2 animate-on-scroll">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-pie bento-icon text-blue-400"></i>
                    <h3 class="bento-title">Detailed Expense Breakdowns</h3>
                    <p class="bento-text">
                      Track your daily spending and get a clear, visual
                      breakdown of your expenses each month. See exactly where
                      your money goes.
                    </p>
                    <img
                      src="img/month.png"
                      onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/800x400/18181b/3f3f46?text=Monthly+UI';"
                      alt="Dashboard UI"
                      class="bento-image-large"
                    />
                  </div>

                  <!-- Card 2: Privacy -->
                  <div
                    class="bento-card animate-on-scroll"
                    style="--delay: 0.1s"
                  >
                    <i class="fas fa-user-shield bento-icon text-green-400"></i>
                    <h3 class="bento-title">
                      100% Private - With Optional Cloud Sync
                    </h3>
                    <p class="bento-text">
                      By default, all data is stored exclusively in your browser
                      using localStorage. You can optionally enable secure Cloud
                      Sync (powered by Supabase) to backup your data.
                      <button
                        id="open-privacy-policy"
                        class="transition-colors underline font-medium hover:text-orange-500"
                      >
                        Read the privacy policy here.
                      </button>
                    </p>
                    <!-- THIS DIV WAS MISSING AND HAS BEEN RESTORED -->
                    <div
                      class="mt-4 flex justify-center items-center h-full bg-grid-pattern rounded-lg"
                    >
                      <i class="fas fa-lock text-6xl text-green-400/50"></i>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Bottom Row -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                  <div
                    class="bento-card animate-on-scroll"
                    style="--delay: 0.2s"
                  >
                    <i
                      class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd bento-icon text-red-400"
                    ></i>
                    <h3 class="bento-title">Debts & Receivables</h3>
                    <p class="bento-text">
                      Easily track who you owe and who owes you. Never lose
                      track of a friendly loan again.
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div
                    class="bento-card animate-on-scroll"
                    style="--delay: 0.3s"
                  >
                    <i class="fas fa-sliders-h bento-icon text-orange-400"></i>
                    <h3 class="bento-title">Fully Customizable</h3>
                    <p class="bento-text">
                      Rename accounts, add or remove expense categories, and set
                      credit card limits. Make Kaasi truly yours.
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div
                    class="bento-card animate-on-scroll"
                    style="--delay: 0.4s"
                  >
                    <i
                      class="fas fa-file-export bento-icon text-purple-400"
                    ></i>
                    <h3 class="bento-title">Data Management</h3>
                    <p class="bento-text">
                      Your data is yours. Export and import your entire
                      financial history with a single click.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- What's Next Section -->
          <section id="whats-next" class="py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
              <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2
                  class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 animate-on-scroll"
                >
                  Always Getting Better
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="text-lg text-gray-400 animate-on-scroll"
                  style="--delay: 0.1s"
                >
                  Kaasi is actively developed. Here's what's on the horizon.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto"
              >
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll">
                  <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                  <h3>Device Installation</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Install Kaasi directly to your home screen for an offline, native experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.1s">
                  <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                  <h3>Themes & Accents</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Personalize the app with custom colors and a crisp new Light Mode.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.2s">
                  <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i>
                  <h3>PIN Lock Security</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Adding a secure 4-digit PIN lock to keep your financial data strictly private.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.3s">
                  <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
                  <h3>Category Budgets</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Set and track monthly spending limits for specific categories.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.4s">
                  <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i>
                  <h3>Inbuilt Calculator</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Perform simple math directly inside amount input fields.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.5s">
                  <i class="fas fa-cloud-arrow-up"></i>
                  <h3>Cloud Backups</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Optional, automatic cloud backups so you never lose your data.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.6s">
                  <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
                  <h3>Dashboard Layout</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">More ways to declutter your dashboard by hiding unused sections.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.7s">
                  <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
                  <h3>Credit Cards</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Refining the interface to make tracking card payments effortless.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.8s">
                  <i class="fas fa-eye-slash"></i>
                  <h3>Hidden Categories</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Exclude specific transaction categories from your charts and reports.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 0.9s">
                  <i class="fas fa-bars-progress"></i>
                  <h3>Debt Progress</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Dynamic visual progress bars to help track partial payments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 1.0s">
                  <i class="fas fa-filter"></i>
                  <h3>Advanced Search</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Building granular date, amount, and category filters.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="next-feature-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 1.1s">
                  <i class="fas fa-hand-pointer"></i>
                  <h3>Mobile Experience</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm">Interaction improvements designed for a premium mobile feel.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- From the Blog Section -->
          <section
            id="blog-section"
            class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-gray-900/20 border-y border-gray-800/60"
          >
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
              <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2
                  class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 animate-on-scroll"
                >
                  From the Blog
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="text-lg text-gray-400 animate-on-scroll"
                  style="--delay: 0.1s"
                >
                  Financial insights, app updates, and guides to help you master
                  your money.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                id="recent-posts-container"
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"
              >
                {% set posts = collections.post | reverse %}

                
                {% for post in posts.slice(0, 3) %}
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="blog-card animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: {{ loop.index0 * 0.1 }}s">
                    <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="blog-card-image" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/18181b/3f3f46?text=Image+Not+Found';">
                    <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                        <span class="blog-card-date">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span>
                        <h3 class="blog-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                        <p class="blog-card-excerpt mt-auto">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                {% endfor %}


              </div>
              <div
                class="text-center mt-12 animate-on-scroll"
                style="--delay: 0.3s"
              >
                <a href="/blog/" class="cta-button-secondary">
                  View All Posts <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Project Story Section -->
          <section id="story" class="py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
              <img
                src="img/AanjeloNoText.svg"
                alt="Aanjelo Salgado Logo"
                class="h-12 mx-auto mb-6 animate-on-scroll"
                onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/100x48/121212/e67e26?text=AS&font=satoshi';"
              />
              <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 animate-on-scroll"
                style="--delay: 0.1s"
              >
                From a Personal Need to a Public Tool
              </h2>
              <div
                class="text-lg text-gray-400 space-y-4 animate-on-scroll"
                style="--delay: 0.2s"
              >
                <p>
                  For about three years, I managed my finances in a Google
                  Sheet. It was my trusted system because most budgeting apps
                  missed key features, had ads, or raised privacy concerns.
                </p>
                <p>
                  So, I started experimenting with AI tools to build my own
                  solution. After about 20 days and dozens of iterations with
                  Google's Gemini, Kaasi was born. It's the tool I always
                  wanted: simple, powerful, completely private, and still
                  improving. I built Kaasi for myself, but I hope it can help
                  you manage your
                  <span class="text-orange-500 font-semibold">කාසි</span>
                  better, too.
                </p>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-300">- Aanjelo Salgado</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Donate Section -->
          <section
            id="donate"
            class="py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-gray-800/60"
          >
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
              <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                  Support Kaasi's Development
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
                  Your donation helps keep Kaasi free and in active development.
                  Since the AI subscriptions used for development are quite
                  expensive, and I want to keep Kaasi free for everyone, your
                  kind support is greatly appreciated!
                </p>
                <button id="donate-button" class="cta-button-large">
                  Show Bank Details
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>